MOBILE UX SAFEGUARDS (MANDATORY)

Sticky progress indicator at top

Sticky ‚ÄúContinue‚Äù button on long screens

Keyboard-aware spacing (no fields hidden)

Autofocus next field

Clear error states (one at a time)

FINAL MOBILE TEST (PASS / FAIL)

The flow is correct only if:

Each screen can be completed in under 20 seconds

No screen feels overwhelming

A homeowner can complete the form one-handed

Nothing feels like a ‚Äúsales funnel‚Äù